Package: chompR
Type: Package
Title: ChIP and ATAC-seq data processing pipeline
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: c(person("Anil", "Chalisey", , "anilchalisey@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre")))
Maintainer: Anil Chalisey <anilchalisey@gmail.com>
Description: An R-based pipeline to analyse chromatin modification high throughput 
  sequencing data. This pipeline performs quality control of reads, performs peak-calling, 
  differential peak-calling, and pathway enrichment analyses.
Depends: R (>= 3.4.0)
SystemRequirements: FastQC, MultiQC, fastp, samtools, sambamba, hisat2, MACS2, featureCounts
License: GPL-3 + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
